---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken Burrito Bowl with Radish Salsa, Cheddar Cheese & Garlic Aioli
description: We think burritos are even better in a bowl, don’t you? That way you can mix up all the elements, like juicy Tex-Mex chicken, zingy salsa and fragrant garlic rice for the perfect bite. Or, you can enjoy them on their own, savouring their separate flavours. Either way, it’s a winner for us!
